Package com.project.springbootjavafx.repositories

package com.project.springbootjavafx.repositories
  • Interfaces
    Class
    Description
    CenyRepository
    The CenyRepository interface provides methods for performing CRUD operations on Ceny entities as well as a custom query to retrieve pricing information based on a trip type.
    HoteleRepository
    The HoteleRepository interface provides data access operations for the Hotele entity.
    KlienciRepository
    The KlienciRepository interface provides data access operations for the Klienci entity.
    ListaNocyHoteliRepository
    The ListaNocyHoteliRepository interface provides data access operations for the ListaNocyHoteli entity.
    ListyHoteliRepository
    The ListyHoteliRepository interface provides data access operations for the ListyHoteli entity, which is identified by a composite key ListyHoteliKey.
    MiastaRepository
    The MiastaRepository interface provides CRUD operations for the Miasta entity.
    MiastaWycieczekRepository
    The MiastaWycieczekRepository interface provides CRUD operations and custom query methods for the MiastaWycieczek entity.
    PokojeRepository
    The PokojeRepository interface provides data access operations for the Pokoje entity.
    TypyWycieczekRepository
    The TypyWycieczekRepository interface provides CRUD operations for the TypyWycieczek entity, as well as custom query methods for related operations.
    WycieczkiRepository
    The WycieczkiRepository interface provides CRUD operations for the Wycieczki entity.
